lead_paragraph: Coming off consecutive victories over ranked teams, No. 5 Ohio State got off to a slow start in a 97-70 victory over unranked Indiana on Thursday night.

headline.print_headline: Mitchell, Cooper Lead No. 5 Ohio St Women Over Indiana
